com.tedros.fxapi.presenter.model

Class TModelView<M extends ITModel>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tedros.fxapi.presenter.model.TModelView<M>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITModelView<M>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BackgroundImageModelView, EntidadeProperty, LoginModelView, PainelModelView, TEntityModelView, TFilterModelView

    public abstract class TModelView<M extends ITModel>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITModelView<M>

    This engine can bind all javafx property between a TModelView and a ITModel, listeners are build to listen changes in the propertys and set the new values in the ITModel.

    Sample Usage

     
 // The model
 public class ExampleModel implements ITModel {
 
    private Long id;
    ...
    private String name;
    private BigDecimal value;
    private Date date;
    ...         
   // getters and setters
 }
 
 // The TModelView
 public class ExampleModelView extends TModelView<ExampleModel>{
  
    private SimpleLongProperty id;
    ...
    private SimpleStringProperty name;
    private SimpleObjectProperty<BigDecimal> value;
    private SimpleObjectProperty<Date> date;
    
    public ExampleModelView(ExampleModel model) {
      super(model);
    }
    ...
    // getters and setters
  }
    Author:
    Davis Gordon
